Now I have no attorney.

01:13:00.166 --> 01:13:01.250
Hmm.

01:13:04.458 --> 01:13:06.625
Gee, that's a very,
very nice outfit.

01:13:08.708 --> 01:13:09.750
Thank you.

01:13:12.792 --> 01:13:13.917
Do you like it here?

01:13:14.583 --> 01:13:17.125
(SIGHS) Mr. Miller,
I'll make you a promise.

01:13:17.792 --> 01:13:19.959
When we're all through,
if you still want to
know about me,

01:13:19.959 --> 01:13:21.375
I'll be more than
happy to tell you.

01:13:21.375 --> 01:13:24.959
But right now,
let's concentrate
on you, all right?

01:13:26.000 --> 01:13:27.166
Good morning!

01:13:27.834 --> 01:13:29.750
Well, well.
Look who's here.

01:13:29.750 --> 01:13:31.750
Good morning.
I missed you.

01:13:31.750 --> 01:13:32.959
How are you, buddy?

01:13:32.959 --> 01:13:34.000
What do you care?

01:13:34.000 --> 01:13:35.333
Oh, stop it.

01:13:35.333 --> 01:13:37.417
You think I let
you down, don't you?

01:13:38.083 --> 01:13:40.083
Where were you?
I'm just curious.

01:13:40.291 --> 01:13:41.834
I'd tell you,
but you wouldn't understand.

01:13:42.125 --> 01:13:44.291
Don't treat me
like a moron. Try me.

01:13:45.458 --> 01:13:47.834
I was trapped
near the inner
circle of thought.

01:13:48.708 --> 01:13:50.667
I don't understand.
I told you.

01:13:51.834 --> 01:13:53.041
Good morning.

01:13:53.041 --> 01:13:54.542
Morning.
Morning.

01:13:55.875 --> 01:13:57.708
Hi. How are you?

01:13:57.708 --> 01:13:59.166
Good morning, everybody.

01:13:59.834 --> 01:14:01.959
Let's begin.
Miss Foster, you're up.

01:14:02.834 --> 01:14:04.333
Thank you, Your Honors.

01:14:05.333 --> 01:14:07.417
This morning,

01:14:07.417 --> 01:14:10.291
l would like to begin
in the 34th year of life.

01:14:11.542 --> 01:14:13.667
Mr. Miller had accepted
a speaking engagement

01:14:13.667 --> 01:14:17.375
to represent
all of the West Coast
advertising agencies

01:14:17.375 --> 01:14:20.500
in a very important speech
to the Ford Motor Company.

01:14:21.333 --> 01:14:23.917
A situation where
if he did well,

01:14:23.917 --> 01:14:26.208
it could have worked
wonders for his career.

01:14:26.542 --> 01:14:28.500
Let's not make this
the end of the world, okay?

01:14:29.083 --> 01:14:31.834
May we go to
34-7-7, please?

01:14:32.834 --> 01:14:33.834
(BEEPING)

01:14:37.500 --> 01:14:40.542
It's packed
like sardines.
Are you ready?

01:14:41.250 --> 01:14:43.041
